texts.text: I-It's done! It's perfect...
>A huge magic circle is drawn on the ground...
And it's no longer lopsided because I've had a lot of practice!
Now comes the hard part. The summoner has to make an offering of their own blood as sacrifice...
I don't like pain, but I guess it does make sense to use one's own blood as sacrifice...
And this is to make Dominion my guardian angel, so no sacrifice is too great...
Here goes!
>The woman cuts her arm with a knife!
>Blood starts to flow down her arm and drip to the ground...
>The blood courses through the lines of the magic circle as it starts to glow!
OMG, it really looks like I'm going to succeed this time! Umm...
Come forth, for I am in need of you. I offer you my life's blood as a token of our pact.
Come forth, ye who would answer my call!
>In response to the woman's chant, something starts to appear in the magic circle.
Wait, what...?

That's not my darling Dominion...
Oh shit. this looks bad...
Aaah, this is the moment I've been waiting for!
The summoning of Rangda! Now I can make a pact with the witch queen and
curse the fools who made fun of me!
I will rain terror on my enemies!
Hey, you're that guy...
Umm, this looks kinda bad. Did I screw up again?
No, you succeeded.
You performed the ritual correctly using the right magic circle. And you used yourself as sacrifice.
You have successfully summoned Rangda, the wicked witch of the dark arts.
Use myself as sacrifice? But I'm the summoner, my blood was the sacrifice...

My blood...
*groan*
It's still flowing towards the circle. The bleeding's not stopping...
This method for summoning Rangda will cost you your life.
It was written on that book I gave you, right?
Oh, I almost forgot. I tore out that page before giving it to you.

W-What... That's awful...
*Pant*

Can't stand...
So cold...
That's the spirit, sacrificial maiden!
You're life's blood will call forth Rangda!
Don't worry, I'll give you a grand burial after it's all over.
...What's this?
Found you! You're the guy behind all this!
What the hell is that?! Something's trying to come out, and there's a woman lying there!
Who... Oh, you're the ones who were sniffing around this girl's hobby projects.
I won't let you stop me. Not when I'm so close!
>The man throws a piece of paper at the Liberators, and demons emerge from the magic circle drawn on it!
*Screech*
*Growl*
Shit... Take'em out fast yo! We gotta stop that demon from comin' out!
Got it! Devil Download!
(So I'm going to die...)
(I feel cold and drowsy, and my body's going numb...)
(Everything's so dark...)
What the... Where did YOU come from?!
Begone, vile witch!
No! Don't interfere!
Know that you will never set foot on this plain!
(Is that... Dominion?)
...o, Yo! Wake up yo!!

You're awake! Thank god.
You okay miss?
Where... I...
Yesssss!! She's alive!!

I... I thought I died...
Ouch. I'm bandaged...?
Yes, but try to stay still.
It's just a quick patch-up, you'll need to go to a hospital later.

That guy and the witch Rangda...
What happened?
The ritual was stopped.
The guy summoning her ran off with the book after he saw the summon was not going to work.
Okay...
Now it's my turn to ask a question. Mind telling me what the hell happened here?

Let me get this straight...
You fell in love with the angel Dominion,
so you tried every way you can find to summon him?
Then you tried the summon from the book that guy gave you, and all hell broke loose. That it?
Yes...
So the wierd lookin' magic circles we've been finding was your doing.
Dang it man. Gotta hand it to ya. You're a woman of action.
But ain't none of that gonna matter if you die, is it?
You're right. I'm sorry for all the trouble I caused.
There's one more thing though... I think I saw Dominion before I passed out, did you...
...Beats me. We ain't seen nothing.
I see...
Hey, shouldn't we tell her he actually came to the rescue?
...Megakin probably thinks it's best not to.
He doesn't want her to be involved with demons anymore. He's doing her a favor.
Yeah, I guess you're right.
Anyways, dealing with demons is a dangerous thing, especially for those who can't fight.
So no more experiments on summoning demons, aight?
Hmm, so you're saying that you guys can fight those monsters?
Huh? Well yeah. But not everyone has the...
Then if I'm with you, I can do as many experiments as I want, right?
Until I summon Dominion that is.
Say what?
I'm not wrong, am I?
If the experiment fails and something bad is summoned, you guys will handle it, right?
Then this is a big step forward for me!
Now I can do any summon I want, even the dangerous ones that I was afraid of trying!
Yo, just wait a minute girl. Weren't you listenin' to me?
Oh, I'll pay you of course!
That's not what I mean...
Oh my darling Dominion. My guardian angel to be...

I will not give up!
I'm going to double my efforts!
...Oh god, I give up.
